When you create the deployment for any Application you choose two manadatory item
1. Deplyment Group
2. New revision location
    It could be S3 or Github
    
    You can also provide below optional setting
    1. ApplicationStop lifecycle event failure:-
          If enabled then the Deployment will keep going on the instance even if '
          pplicationStop' Hook failed.
    2. Encoutering file of same name on new and old version of application.
       There is 3 option
       1. Fail the deployment
       2. Overwrite the content
       3. Retain the content
   3. You can override the rollback setting of deployment group.

        
